  <description>
    <p>**NOTE: This wrapper is not verified by, affiliated with, or supported by Asapha Halifa.**</p>
    <p>Stream your music, listen to your movies, hear your games or use your phone as mic.</p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Turn your phone into a wireless speaker or headset for your computer.</li>
      <li>Use a USB connection to get the best experience possible.</li>
      <li>Send your music to multiple rooms, wirelessly listen with multiple people.</li>
      <li>Your PC audio is sent in realtime. Experience lower latency than with Bluetooth.</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
